items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 480 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 97!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 185 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 38!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 500 checkins with the serving style of Can. You have reached the top!! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 170 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 35!
